Typedef Documentation

typedef int(* jmi_residual_func_t)(jmi_t *jmi, jmi_ad_var_vec_p res)

Function signature for evaluation of a residual function in the generated code.

Notice that this function signature is used for all functions in the DAE, DAE initialization, and Optimization interfaces. Notice that this definition supports both C compilation and C++ compilation with CppAD.

Parameters:
jmi A jmi_t struct.
res (Output) The residual value.
Returns:
Error code.
